Appman
======

Appman lets you easily check on your remote servers.
Its usage is directly inspired by heroku, but works on any server.

- Commands

help # this message
releases # view the last releases in your app dir
logs # print your latest logs
run # run bash in your app dir

- Info

github.com/colinyoung/appman
@colinyoung

GPL v2, feel free to fork!
